data.description: EXTENDED GARAGE, Upgraded tile throughout, 8' doors, Tile Backsplash, Double glass den doors, Ceiling fans t/o, FARM SINK, Upgraded cabinetry w/ soft close & pullout shelves, Walk-in Showers, Wrought Iron Entry door, laundry cabinets~just to mention a few of the MANY upgrades!! This home is a haven of comfort & serenity~designed for those seeking the perfect blend of relaxation & community. Tranquil setting(NO neighbors behind) & easy access to all essentials(Shopping centers, Gyms, Restaurants, & all of Encore's amenities! Ensuring a convenient, enjoyable, active 55+ lifestyle). Step outside & enjoy inviting outdoor spaces~entertain friends on the Xtnd'd covered patio & front porch(gas stub inc.) Inside, you'll discover an interior adorned w/ tasteful upgrades & soothing color palettes.
